      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
        <docTitle refersTo="#adoption">Adopted by the Security Council at its <inline name="adoptionMeeting" title="5429th">5429th meeting</inline>, on<docDate date="2006-04-27" refersTo="#adoptionDate">27 April 2006</docDate></docTitle>
